item.title: Stuck 0o
item.dc:creator: @6aceofspades 6aceofspades
item.description:
@6aceofspades wrote:

A problem that alot of people have been having with this development kit is how they download it. Don’t check the box next to your choice of download but click on it as a link… hard to explain but if you LOOK at it, it should be self explanitory (sp?).

But incase that’s not your problem just listen to that guy. ^^ The offline package will dl the whole thing onto your comp right away. The online one will open up a seperate online installer and install that way, it’s confusing but just dl the offline one and save yourself a headache.

-Justin

P.S. Don’t forget to click “Accept” at the very top of the page of the SDK download section.
P.S.S Sorry if this is a bit confusing it’s late. -.-
